urant “La Grenouillère” near Montreuil-sur-Mer in the Pas-de-Calais region.\r\nThere, I elaborate a unique, authentic, signature cuisine. I humbly anchor it in my region, in the Côte d’Opale which I explore in all its aspects, natural and human. I offer a true French-rooted contemporary cuisine, freed of its convictions and its prejudice.\r\nIn 2009, I entrusted the architect Patrick Bouchain with the renovation of the restaurant, to make it into a place of today. I strive for more, such as La Grenouillère being more than just a great restaurant.\r\nLa Grenouillère is a house of freedom and expression for those who live in it and live it with me.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" offset=\"vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs\"][vc_single_image image=\"120\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"bottom-to-top\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Chef','','publish','closed','closed','','chef','','','2016-01-04 18:15:58','2016-01-04 17:15:58','',600,'http://www.lagrenouillere.fr/?page_id=576',0,'page','',0),(577,2,'2016-01-04 13:19:21','2016-01-04 12:19:21','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" offset=\"vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs\"][vc_single_image image=\"120\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bottom-to-top\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Alexandre Gauthier</h3>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Chef</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I was born a chef.\r\nIn 2003, I to